File and Content Report
Generate a report about files uploaded to your organization.
FIELD DESCRIPTION
Archived
Flag that indicates whether a file has been archived.
Title
Title of a file, content pack, Google doc, or Web link.
Created By
User who uploaded the file, content pack, Google Doc, or Web link.
File and Content Report Fields
Field Description
Title Title of a file, content pack, Google doc, or Web link.
Archived Flag that indicates whether a file has been archived.
Created By User who uploaded the file, content pack, Google Doc, or Web link.
Tips for Using File and Content Reports
Salesforce CRM Content users can sort report data by library they have access to or all libraries in an organization.
Sort custom reports by Library Name to view data for individual files as well as library summaries.
Sort according to the Content ID to view data for a particular document.
title: Understanding File and Content Reports in Salesforce
